8/05/21/chao-mung-15-nam-wp-da-dien-ra-tai-nha-trang/33131701_1772135246162903_3304438960121446400_o/\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33131701_1772135246162903_3304438960121446400_o-300x169.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33131701_1772135246162903_3304438960121446400_o-300x169.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33131701_1772135246162903_3304438960121446400_o-768x432.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33131701_1772135246162903_3304438960121446400_o-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://vi.wordpress.org/2018/05/21/chao-mung-15-nam-wp-da-dien-ra-tai-nha-trang/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o/\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33141783_1772135922829502_3595800775453835264_o-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://vi.wordpress.org/2018/05/21/chao-mung-15-nam-wp-da-dien-ra-tai-nha-trang/33180095_1772135459496215_1390434999961911296_o/\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33180095_1772135459496215_1390434999961911296_o-300x169.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33180095_1772135459496215_1390434999961911296_o-300x169.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/05/33180095_1772135459496215_1390